prompts.frontCover: Cartoon illustration of the couple from the reference photo, transformed into astronauts floating weightlessly in a dreamy, fantastical outer space. Lao Lao, on the left, has a joyous, wide-eyed expression as she playfully tries to catch a floating, glowing star with one hand while holding a space helmet under her other arm. Jordan, on the right, is laughing as he holds onto a giant, cartoonish three-tiered birthday cake that's cleverly designed as a rocket ship, complete with frosting engines leaving a trail of sparkling sprinkles. Their astronaut suits are modern and sleek, customized with their sweatshirt colors from the photo: Lao Lao's is light blue and Jordan's is tan. The background is a cosmic wonderland filled with whimsical pastel planets swirled with watercolor textures, soft glowing nebulae in shades of pink and lavender, and twinkling star constellations. In the center, the words "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" are written in a beautiful, flowing, and easily readable handwritten cursive script, glowing with a soft white light. The overall style is flat 2D artwork, whimsical, humorous, and full of ethereal magic.
